### Fetch all tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

### Create new task
POST http://localhost:3000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "vvxv",
    "date": "2021-01-01T12:00:00Z",
    "description": "fgfhfhfhfh",
    "priority": "normal",
    "status": "todo"
}

### Update a task

PUT http://localhost:3000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": "9a628de3-06cd-466b-b16c-096582c0e536",
    "status": "todo"
}